== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Aletta 2006 track.png}}
2006年5月21日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]进入[[太平洋|东太平洋]]。东风波向西移动，于数天后开始同[[特万特佩克湾|特万特佩克湾]]附近的下层[[低压槽|低压槽]]相互影响，促使系统内的深层对流增长。到了5月25日，[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]以南数百英里外已经有大规模[[低气压|低气压区]]形成。系统起初受[[风切变|风切变]]影响导致发展缓慢，但外部环境在数天后略有改善。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月27日早上6点，[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]的第一{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压在阿卡普尔科以南约305公里洋面形成。<ref name="tcr">{{Cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | title = Tropical Storm Aletta Tropical Cyclone Report | year = 2006 | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2013-12-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215201856/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP012006_Aletta.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP012006_Aletta.pdf | archivedate = 2013-12-15 | date =  }}</ref>

低气压的移动幅度很小，并因风切变的持续存在导致结构混乱，环流中心位于对流活动以西<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115822/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.001.shtml | author = Avila | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Number 1 | year = 2006 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.001.shtml? | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。到了5月27日上午，系统开始表现出总体结构继续组织的迹象，主要是东部半圆内的对流出现爆发。与此同时，环流中心或是经过重组，或是开始向北面（可能是[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]）移动。受[[高压脊|高压脊]]的转向气流影响，大部分预测结果都认为风暴会保持北上数天，但也有部分[[热带气旋预报|计算机模型]]预计气旋会从阿卡普尔科附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。<ref>{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Number 2 | year = 2006 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.002.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115823/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-11-08 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}5月27日下午18点，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]把第一{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“阿莱塔”（{{lang|en|Aletta}}）为其命名<ref name="tcr" />。

气象机构对风暴的预测一直存在困难<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch | title = Tropical Storm Aletta Discussion Number 4 | year = 2006 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115826/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.004.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>，阿莱塔中心以东于5月28日爆发出新的对流带，气旋同时开始蜿蜒南下<ref>{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Aletta Discussion Number 5 | year = 2006 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115841/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}早上6点，风暴几乎停止前进，并达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]72公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。当天下午，阿莱塔的中心模糊不清，所以只能估计其确切位置。此外，环流结构因风切变的强度变化而波动，云层格局不再是热带气旋典型的环型，而变得更加拉长<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Aletta Discussion Number 7 | year = 2006 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115843/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.007.shtml? }}</ref>。风暴向西飘移，移动路径到5月29日清晨已形成小规模环路。受风切变增加、干燥空气侵入环流的共同影响，阿莱特于{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。此后系统内保留的对流很少<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch | title = Tropical Depression Aletta Discussion Number 12 | year = 2006 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.012.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115903/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep01/ep012006.discus.012.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>，坚持两天后于5月31日退化成残留低气压，并在之后不久完全消散<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
风暴开始朝墨西哥移动时，该国政府向[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]蓬塔马尔多纳多（{{lang|en|Punta Maldonado}}）到[[锡瓦塔内霍|锡瓦塔内霍]]之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref name="SMN Aletta">{{cite web | author = Alberto Hernández Unzón | author2 = M. G. Cirilo Bravo Lujano | publisher = Servicio Meteorologico Nacional, Comisión Nacional del Agua | title = Resúmen de la Tormenta Tropical Aletta del Océano Pacífico | archivedate = 2009-03-27 | deadurl = yes | url = http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2006/pacifico/aletta/aletta.pdf | accessdate = 2009-03-27 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327033905/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2006/pacifico/aletta/aletta.pdf }}</ref>。风暴强度和前进方向经过一系列变更后，观察预警于{{lang|en|UTC}}5月29日下午18点取消<ref name="tcr" />。

阿莱塔在墨西哥多地产生中等程度降水，[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]雅卡特佩克（{{lang|en|Jacatepec}}）的24小时雨量达到100.2毫米，格雷罗州的卡拉雷也有96毫米<ref name="SMN Aletta" />。大风刮倒部分树木，还引发轻度结构性破坏。锡瓦塔内霍一艘载有9人的船可能因遭遇风暴导致的恶劣海况而失踪，幸运的是船上人员全部获救。<ref>{{cite web |author=Staff Writer |title=Afecta tormenta Aletta a Guerrero |date=2006-05-30 |publisher=El Siglo De Torreon |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151108165052/https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/216214.afecta-tormenta-aletta-a-guerrero |url=https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/216214.afecta-tormenta-aletta-a-guerrero |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-11-09 |archivedate=2015-11-08 }}</ref>没有报道表明这场风暴有造成人员丧生<ref name="tcr" />。

